CA...Heat Advisory until 7 PM PDT this evening for CAZ510-514-515.

PZ...Small Craft Advisory from 3 PM this afternoon to 3 AM PDT
     Wednesday for Pt Pinos to Pt Piedras Blancas 0-10 nm.

     Small Craft Advisory until 3 AM PDT Wednesday for Pigeon Pt to
     Pt Pinos 10-60 NM-Pt Arena to Pt Reyes 10-60 NM.

